1.0.name: wordpress/whispy
1.0.description: Whispy is a sharp, lime-ish theme resting on the solid bones of Twenty Ten. Tweaked for improved SEO performance, it features an optional three-column template, optional no-header formatting and the ability to specify title and description text colour.
